*.jsonl filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
# LFS for PDFs is scoped to own-artefact directories only (corpus-management-plan
# v0.2.1 item 4): a blanket *.pdf rule once swept a publisher supplement into
# public history (2026-07-13 purge). Third-party PDFs live out-of-tree — see
# corpus/README.md.
docs/**/*.pdf filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
**/reproduction/**/*.pdf filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
**/prereg/*.pdf filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
